header.name: Castle of Arana-Nalarax
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: After being destroyed in a devastating battle a long time ago the castle of Arana-Nalarax remained deserted. Recently it was squatted by a gang of orcs. Rumors say that countless treasures of magical artifacts are stored here.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A large double door on the southern wall of the large room.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A dying barbarian, a spear, a scarf and some gold among his belongings.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: A confident hooded bard. Wants to join you.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A mundane-looking door, wails loudly when the knob is touched.
